question: Whats is the office sector demand with commercial leasing activity in the major cities of India in 2019?
explanation: In 2019, office sector demand with commercial leasing activity reached 69.4 msf. The Co-working space across top seven cities increased to reach 12 sq ft by end of 2019. Office space has been driven mostly by growth in ITeS/IT, BFSI, consulting and manufacturing sectors.
